BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 156.72 610 Td (UNDERSTANDING GRIEF) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 0.5 w 50 598 m 382 598 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 50 575 Td (Grief is not stages. It is waves.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 50 561 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 50 547 Td (Some days the waves are gentle. Some days they knock) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 50 533 Td (you down. Both are normal. Both are grief.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 50 519 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 50 505 Td (There is no timeline. There is no 'getting over it.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 50 491 Td (There is only learning to carry it differently.) Tj ET
